Adding something like this though, will generate the necessary specialization.

{code}
class Blah[@specialized (Int) T:Manifest](a:T) {
  def blah[@specialized (Int) S>:T, @specialized (Int)  W:Manifest](f:S=>W):W  =f(a) 
}
{code}

